Biography

Joe Jonas is the middle child in a sibling trio band called the Jonas brothers. Of course, if you have a child, sibling, cousin, who is a girl under 17, you already know this. Seems all worlds a buzz about Joe Jonas, and with good cause, this is a talented and well presented teenager.

Originally Joe wanted to be a stand up comedian. His brothers however, are both musical as are his parents, and he was persuaded to join the practicing that eventually took off into a career that would launch him to stardom.

In 2008 Joe starred in the Disney Camp Rock Movie The movie was seen by more than 8.9 million viewers !

Joe grew up in New Jersey, with an older brother, Kevin, and two younger brothers, Nick and Frankie. Their father is an ordained minister and their mother a sign language teacher who home schooled her children and instilled a love of music in her boys.
